About
Located just 20 minutes from central Dubai, the Dubai Autodrome Circuit is an FIA Grade 1 race circuit that incorporates various different experiences for kids, adults and families - these include: - our Race & Drive Center, where you can enjoy the thrill of driving various road and race cars on the circuit. -Indoor and Outdoor Kartdrome for kids aged from 7 years and upwards -Lasertag center -Motorsport Events, Dubai Autodrome hosts national and international sporting events including the famous 24H Dubai race Asian Le Mans Series & The Gulf Historic Dubai GP Revival.
Duration: 1-2 hours

    Formula DXB Max Experience
    I did the Formula DXB Max experience and thoroughly loved it! My instructor, Fidel, gave a great briefing prior to driving and answered all questions. After the session, Kuda gave me instruction on how I could improve my driving, which was much appreciated. I will be back soon! One area could be improved on, which is the lighting at night.   • Bary M
    1 contribution
    F1 Experience 11/10
    I did the F1 track experience and it was worth every penny. My instructor Sean was very thorough and informative. He started by briefing me on what to expect followed by driving me around the track in a BMW M3 for familiarization. I then drove a couple laps in a 2-seater racecar as Sean rode along, in order to get me comfortable on the track. This gave me a chance to get familiar with braking zones and corner exits before hopping into the beast. Then there was the F1 drive itself. I definitely stalled out a couple times leaving the pit lane, but the engineers were very helpful in getting me moving. By far the best driving experience I've had. If you ever get the opportunity, this is something you don't want to miss. This was my first time on a race track. I hadn't driven a manual car any time recently, but I do a lot of sim racing. You definitely want to be comfortable with when to shift, but the clutch is only used for getting into 1st gear. Once you get going, it's all paddle shifters from there. This was a blast, and I highly recommend Sean as an instructor.
    Dubai Autodrome
    Hello Bary! Thank you for taking the time to write this review. We are very glad you enjoyed the ultimate experience! We will send Sean your regards, and we look forward to your next visit and your next exciting experience. Regards, Dubai Autodrome Team

Ajith Kumar (born 1 May 1971) is an Indian actor who works predominantly in Tamil cinema. To date, he has starred in over 61 films, and won four Vijay Awards, three Cinema Express Awards, three Filmfare Awards South and three Tamil Nadu State Film Awards. In addition to his acting career, Ajith is also a sports car racer and participated in the MRF Racing series (2010). He became a race car driver, competing in circuits around India in places such as Mumbai, Chennai and Delhi. He is one among very few Indians to race in the International arena and in Formula championships. Здравствуйте, Дубае нет привычных нам улиц и номеров домов. Чтобы найти дом, нужно просто знать его название и/или какое-то примечательное место вблизи, например, "слева от стадиона "Дружба". Пожалуйста, откройте Google maps и найдите "Dubai autodrome". Он находится в районе под названием Motor City, собственно, Motor City так называется благодаря автодрому)
